OL,3,CRefugees helping restore a historic
OL,4,Cpub using traditional plastering skills
OL,6,FA Bristol man is helping restore an
OL,7,Fhistoric pub near Bath while teaching
OL,8,Frefugees an important skill.
OL,10,FDaahir Mohamed came to the UK from
OL,11,FSomalia as a refugee himself and is
OL,12,Fnow a skilled lime plasterer.
OL,14,FHe's currently working on the 500-year-
OL,15,Fold Hop Pole pub in Limpley Stoke,
OL,16,Fwhich was saved from development by
OL,17,Fthe community in 2022.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
