OL,3,CRefugees helping restore a historic
OL,4,Cpub using traditional plastering skills
OL,6,FDaahir said: "So often a person from a
OL,7,Frefugee background spends years for
OL,8,Fwaiting for an answer for their
OL,9,Fstatus, so they can work in the
OL,10,Fcountry, and when they're granted
OL,11,Fthey're left on their own with no
OL,12,Fsupport.
OL,14,F"It just made sense encouraging
OL,15,Findividuals who have already been in
OL,16,Fthis industry before to take this on
OL,17,Fboard.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
