OL,3,CRefugees helping restore a historic
OL,4,Cpub using traditional plastering skills
OL,6,F"Instead of looking elsewhere for
OL,7,Fworkers lets us up-skill our local
OL,8,Frefugees and asylum seekers and
OL,9,Fcommunity."
OL,11,FFor Ayham Aldoghim, who fled Syria for
OL,12,Fthe UK, this training has given him
OL,13,Fhope.
OL,15,FHe said: "I met Daahir a few months
OL,16,Fago but before that I was very unsure
OL,17,Fabout what to do, very confused.
OL,19,F"When I saw him talking about the job
OL,20,FI got very excited and said yes this
OL,21,Fwas the opportunity I was waiting for.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
