OL,3,CRefugees helping restore a historic
OL,4,Cpub using traditional plastering skills
OL,6,F"I'm trying to get better and better
OL,7,Fin this job and Daahir is trying to
OL,8,Fencourage me to do more and more and
OL,9,Flearn quickly.
OL,11,FThe Hop Pole building is 500 years
OL,12,Fold, so traditional lime plaster is
OL,13,Fessential for the conservation of the
OL,14,Fpub.
OL,16,FDaahir's explained that the techniques
OL,17,Fand materials he's using are also part
OL,18,Fof his own history.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
