OL,3,CRefugees helping restore a historic
OL,4,Cpub using traditional plastering skills
OL,6,FHe said: "Growing up in Somalia in my
OL,7,Fearly years I remember living in a
OL,8,Fsmall hut in a small village and every
OL,9,Fyear we would re-plaster the outer
OL,10,Fwalls of the hut with clay plaster and
OL,11,Fcow manure.
OL,13,F"Funnily enough, this is the third
OL,14,Ftime I'm using cow manure as plaster
OL,15,Fon a wall in England and it brings a
OL,16,Flot of connection between my past and
OL,17,Fmy present."
OL,19,FUntil villagers stepped in to buy the
OL,20,Fpub, the Hop Pole was going to be sold
OL,21,Fto developers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
