OL,3,CRefugees helping restore a historic
OL,4,Cpub using traditional plastering skills
OL,6,FOnce secured, the building was so
OL,7,Fderelict it needed the support from a
OL,8,Fwhole community of people to restore
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,FSimon Coombe, from the Save the Hop
OL,12,FPole campaign, said the pub had
OL,13,Falready helped people in many
OL,14,Fdifferent ways.
OL,16,FHe said: "It's already giving back
OL,17,Fenormously where people are giving
OL,18,Fwhatever they can give people are
OL,19,Fcoming with advice, some with
OL,20,Fexpertise, their labour their money.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
