OL,3,CRefugees helping restore a historic
OL,4,Cpub using traditional plastering skills
OL,6,F"They're coming with their skills to
OL,7,Fteach those skills to other people and
OL,8,Fthat's the heartwarming thing about
OL,9,Fthis project people's lives are being
OL,10,Fchanged already in this project.
OL,12,F"It's a meaningful job when you think
OL,13,Fabout the history of the place. It's
OL,14,Fpart of the community here they want
OL,15,Fit as beautiful as it was before and
OL,16,Fwe are working on that."
